 Key Insights
Based on the analysis of 2022 sales data, the following insights were identified:
👩 Women customers are more likely to purchase compared to men (~65%)
🌍 Top 3 states contributing to sales:
Maharashtra
Karnataka
Uttar Pradesh (~35%)
👨‍👩‍👧 Adult age group (30–49 years) contributes the most (~50%)
🛒 Top sales channels:
Amazon
Flipkart
Myntra (~80%)
🎯 Final Conclusion (Business Recommendation)
To improve Vrinda Store sales, the strategy should focus on:
Targeting women customers
Age group: 30–49 years
Location: Maharashtra, Karnataka, and Uttar Pradesh
Marketing via:
Amazon
Flipkart
Myntra
👉 Use ads, offers, and discount coupons on these platforms to increase conversions.
💡 Summary
This analysis shows that focusing on the right audience + right platform can significantly boost sales and business growth.
